Victor Osimhen caught up with Cristiano Ronaldo after Napoli’s 1-0 win against Juventus at the Diego Armando Marodona on Saturday night. Osimhen was replaced in the 75th minute of this encounter at Stadio Diego Armando Maradona, while Ronaldo played the entire game. Osimhen took the chance to pose for a photo and exchanged jerseys with the Juventus star. Saturday’s crucial win has lifted Napoli to fourth place on 40 points from 21 games, a point behind Juventus. AC Milan are top of the standings with 49 points.